What are you grateful for now in your life? Use the space below to reflect.\
Family harmony, work harmony, safety, health, beauty, teamwork, letting go of past, relaxing vacation, weather wont harm, wild animals wont harm, can appreciate beauty of nature. Purpose and a means to enact it. Work has paid off. Mistakes haven't been too costly. Avoided life traps or escaped without permanent injury.\
\
The Stoics believed that nature contained the divine, therefore it was perfect. Spending time in nature and being in harmony with it was essential for them. \
Nature provides lettuce & cucumber at the moment but is all the food we eat, our place to live, medicine, entertainment, shelter, air we breathe, water we drink, wind to cool us, shade to comfort, energy from sun, fuel, fire to cook and transport.\
\
